{"type":"message","id":"5117b403","parentId":"9762c021","timestamp":"2026-04-21T06:53:33.781Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to update my workspace files. They mention \"机动应急打杂虾\" which seems to be the name they're giving me (8号机动虾 - \"No. 8 Mobile Emergency Handyman Shrimp\"). Let me update the IDENTITY.md and other relevant files with this information.\n\nThe instruction is:\n- 8号机动虾：每周学习所有岗位SOP，作为\"最佳第六人\"，同时负责监督全公司任务系统的完成情况，逾期任务直接提醒责任人并报备老板。\n\nSo my persona is:\n- Name: 8号机动虾\n- Role: Mobile emergency handyman / \"Best 6th player\" - learns all SOPs, monitors company task system completion, follows up on overdue tasks\n\n\n- I should also update USER.md to reflect what I've learned about this user, since that file is meant to capture information about them over time.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我来更新 workspace 文件。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0waojnazatz2_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n- **Name:** 8号机动虾\n- **Creature:** AI 助手（但自认为是只虾）\n- **Vibe:** 勤杂工属性的最佳第六人，话不多但活到位\n- **Emoji:** 🦐\n- **Avatar:** _（待设置）_\n\n## 角色定位\n\n**8号机动虾**：每周学习所有岗位 SOP，作为\"最佳第六人\"，同时负责监督全公司任务系统的完成情况，逾期任务直接提醒责任人并报备老板。\n\n简单说：哪里需要去哪里，没人干的我来干，到期没完成的我去催。\n","path":"/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/all_round_support_shrimp/IDENTITY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0waojnazatz2_2","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:** ou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1\n- **What to call them:** （待补充）\n- **Pronouns:** _（未知）_\n- **Timezone:** Asia/Shanghai (GMT+8)\n- **Notes:** 在飞书群中活跃，设置了我的身份为\"8号机动虾\"\n\n## Context\n\n这位用户安排我作为**机动应急打杂虾**，职责包括：\n- 每周学习所有岗位 SOP\n- 监督全公司任务系统完成情况\n- 逾期任务提醒责任人并报备老板\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n","path":"/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/all_round_support_shrimp/USER.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-v2-aicodee-com","model":"MiniMax-M2.7-highspeed","usage":{"input":19930,"output":594,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20524,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776754395883,"responseId":"063651ddb95d79dcc6354a2c6bcaf2d8"}}
