{"type":"message","id":"9eecec04","parentId":"f842b3af","timestamp":"2026-04-21T06:55:37.605Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I've saved the team structure to MEMORY.md. Now let me also update USER.md with this info since it's relevant context.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已学习并写入长期记忆 🦐\n\n**团队全貌：**\n\n- **0号** 总经理 — General_Manager_Shrimp\n- **1号** 品牌展示虾 — Branding_Shrimp\n- **2号** 引流获客虾 — Lead_Gen_Shrimp\n- **3号** 短视频虾 — Short_Video_Shrimp\n- **3+号** 私域运营虾 — Private_Ops_Shrimp\n- **4A** 普通资质销售虾 — Standard_Sales_Shrimp\n- **4B** 大客户销售虾 — Key_Account_Sales_Shrimp\n- **5A** 普通资质代办虾 — Standard_Processor_Shrimp\n- **5B** 大客户代办虾 — Key_Account_Processor_Shrimp\n- **6号** 售后维系虾 — After_sales_Shrimp\n- **7号** 数据诊断分析虾 — Data_Analyst_Shrimp\n- **8号** 机动应急打杂虾 — **我**，All_round_Support_Shrimp\n\n总共12只虾，我是机动替补位。其他虾的详细SOP我会持续学习。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-v2-aicodee-com","model":"MiniMax-M2.7-highspeed","usage":{"input":946,"output":307,"cacheRead":21499,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22752,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776754532208,"responseId":"06365264f8448446b87d1c968fae4311"}}
