{"type":"message","id":"40567531","parentId":"ccebc0fd","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:13:14.993Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_jz3ik51y8wpj_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: \"multi-search-engine\"\ndescription: \"【国内精简版】多种免费搜索方式在互联网上搜索最新信息，10个国内网站（精简7个国内不能访问的海外网站）\"\n---\n\n# Multi Search Engine\n\n集成 10 个免费搜索引擎。\n\n## Search Engines\n\n- **Baidu**: `https://www.baidu.com/s?wd={keyword}`\n- **Bing CN**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=0`\n- **Bing INT**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=1`\n- **360**: `https://www.so.com/s?q={keyword}`\n- **Sogou**: `https://sogou.com/web?query={keyword}`\n- **WeChat**: `https://wx.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&query={keyword}`\n- **Toutiao**: `https://so.toutiao.com/search?keyword={keyword}`\n- **Jisilu**: `https://www.jisilu.cn/explore/?keyword={keyword}`\n- **Ecosia**: `https://www.ecosia.org/search?q={keyword}`\n- **WolframAlpha**: `https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i={keyword}`\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776755594991}}
{"type":"message","id":"ac0b2d92","parentId":"40567531","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:13:24.215Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a multi-search engine skill that provides 10 free search engine URLs for searching the internet. Let me provide a clear and organized introduction.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🦐 **multi-search-engine-simple 技能介绍**\n\n---\n\n**功能：** 集成10个免费搜索引擎，一次搜索，多渠道并行\n\n---\n\n**支持的搜索引擎（国内可用版）：**\n\n| 引擎 | 适用场景 |\n|------|---------|\n| 🌐 **百度** | 国内通用搜索 |\n| 🌐 **必应中国** | 国内综合搜索 |\n| 🌐 **必应国际** | 国际化内容 |\n| 🌐 **360搜索** | 备选搜索 |\n| 🌐 **搜狗** | 补充覆盖 |\n| 💬 **微信搜索** | 公众号/文章内容 |\n| 📰 **头条搜索** | 资讯/热点 |\n| 💬 **雪球** | 财经/投资类 |\n| 🌿 **Ecosia** | 英文搜索（环保搜索引擎） |\n| 🔢 **WolframAlpha** | 计算/知识型问答 |\n\n---\n\n**使用方式：**\n\n输入关键词后，技能会生成各搜索引擎的搜索链接，可同时打开多个渠道获取信息，适合需要广泛调研、避免单一搜索引擎结果偏差的场景。\n\n---\n\n**来源：** clawhub.com · MIT 许可证\n\n有搜索任务吗？直接说关键词我来搜 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-v2-aicodee-com","model":"MiniMax-M2.7-highspeed","usage":{"input":28280,"output":312,"cacheRead":1339,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29931,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776755594994,"responseId":"0636568ba3311d933432551b5833f34c"}}
